    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It's in really nice shape and still has plenty of life left in it! It drives smoothly and has been well-maintained, though it shows a little character from regular use. If you're looking for a dependable, comfy ride that's ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see if it's the right fit!",
      "price": 32500.0,
