    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road. It\u2019s in really great shape and has been well-loved, showing just a bit of character from our adventures together. It runs smoothly and is perfect for anyone looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready to go from day one! I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
